{"tid":623665,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"署方認無圖紙監工","createTime":"2018-04-10T07:51:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T01:36:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"6d19177ab2e78963b8a783e64223d5e5a326b8e6","tid":623665,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T07:51:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180410/20357132?_ga=2.58279528.316505459.1523292553-581282530.1504247435\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180410%2F20357132%3F_ga%3D2.58279528.316505459.1523292553-581282530.1504247435&d=14dy5Za6T0yLZEhG0VygexxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=5936abb8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180410%2F20357132%3F_ga%3D2.58279528.316505459.1523292553-581282530.1504247435&h=52ff2d39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180410/20357132?_ga=2.58279528.316505459.1523292553-581282530.1504247435</a><br />\n<br />\n署方認無圖紙監工<br />\n<br />\n12,180<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180410/large/a0402a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180410%2Flarge%2Fa0402a.gif&h=904e9b40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■鍾錦華到沉管巡視，指無發現移位及滲水。路政署圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港府在今次港珠澳大橋人工島防波堤疑崩塌風波中，被質疑監管工程不力。路政署署長鍾錦華昨多次被問到何時得知扭工字塊擺放方式時，均無正面回應，只稱香港有監管工程，主橋工程則由管理局負責。雖然管理局屬於內地法人組織，但香港有派員擔任管理局副局長，屬高層次監管。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n譚文豪：港府監管力度不足<br />\n<br />\n鍾錦華表示，由三地政府組成的港珠澳大橋三地聯合工作委員會（三地委）每月召開工作會議，管理局若有重要決策和情況會上報，但「唔會事無大小都上報」。至於路政署有否「圖紙」監工，鍾指涉及圖紙數以萬計，僅管理局日常監督承辦商施工方需要圖紙，「我哋冇需要攞圖紙去睇，唔會咁做」。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨立法會議員譚文豪認為，特區政府有責任監管整個工程，但事件延至現在才就事件解畫，可見監管工程力度不足。他指政府至少應派署長級官員擔任大橋管理局副局長，但港方代表僅為高級工程師並不足夠。<br />\n<br />\n土木工程師黎廣德亦指，路政署確認人工島設計曾改動，署方應向管理局索取詳細的模型測試數據，了解前後兩個方案的優劣，「路政署唔可以淨係信晒大橋管理局的說法，就百分百接受就算數」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者羅繼盛  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n指人工島缺口為減沉管負載　 大橋管理局解畫　 路政署照單全收<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n紅隧擬增一條自動繳費通道"},{"pid":"29fc539222a4ee82d648f2efd6e526db03120756","tid":623665,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T07:53:58.000Z","msg":"拎份招標圖紙出黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa5a411ba00c7640f108444a9240fca76b6bf9cc","tid":623665,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29fc539222a4ee82d648f2efd6e526db03120756","tid":623665,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T07:53:58.000Z","msg":"拎份招標圖紙出黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T07:55:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一定畀人屌多幾穫"},{"pid":"22b244f24101a6be11eb60b1842d65449f5600d8","tid":623665,"uid":66496,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T08:00:38.000Z","msg":"「老細 呢個project有成萬張紙 我覺得無需要睇而我亦都唔會做」<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母 依家冇出糧俾你班粉腸咩<br />\n成個路政署咁撚多人咁你都講得出？<br />\n大話都作過個好聽少少啦仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"716cf32d0d6971badaa9a9455ea5cf8069505010","tid":623665,"uid":10064,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T08:02:08.000Z","msg":"幾千億工程無圖紙<br />\n哈哈哈"},{"pid":"5e23fbd8632053259d23743ebc6f97ebd43afea1","tid":62366